Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Loving Los Angeles
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xpr8
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Mar 1986
Time to reconsider that smug, cliched view of the cultured city of Los Angeles. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.